{
  "_id": "k3FMiqj9KhfIHCxGVvImdu",
  "body": [
    {
      "_key": "71688d90-1711-44ee-837c-df1fcebb89ae",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-label-97941cd3-cbc4-4ff8-abce-29db785f1529",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "参考: "
        },
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-link-6f1d07c7-74dd-4731-a81b-5436cda10749",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "link-d65d503b-539c-4acd-9f6b-cb9666f6b5ed"
          ],
          "text": "厚生労働省 医療施設調査"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-d65d503b-539c-4acd-9f6b-cb9666f6b5ed",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/list/79-1.html"
        }
      ],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "1db7248f-9755-4dc0-a230-e3088ff8c9d7",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "bbe2047c-9b23-4775-ad25-7644f0a80363",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "看護助手から看護師へ！働きながら夢を叶えるための現実的な道筋"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "c2f4d1c8-ee8a-4bae-a0ee-08c4f2cce992",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "22c189e3-a26b-40a4-94c3-2e5f079902f8",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "「患者さんにもっと寄り添ったケアがしたい」「専門知識を身につけてキャリアアップしたい」"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "dc53fd26-e18e-44de-83e8-8754e1c56e61",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "324eb007-aae4-4e77-8d25-9a2bf5a8c098",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "看護助手として働く中で、看護師への憧れを抱く方は少なくありません。しかし、仕事を続けながら看護学校に通うことは、時間的にも経済的にも大きな挑戦です。無計画に始めると、仕事と勉強の両立に悩み、挫折してしまう可能性もあります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "9571b437-62f5-4ccc-92b3-12ee3595bc41",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "7e1bbc92-13e9-4ed3-93d0-81ca707e4a52",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "しかし、正しい情報を得て、計画的に準備を進めれば、働きながら看護師になる夢は決して不可能ではありません。この記事では、看護助手から看護師を目指すための具体的なルート、入学準備、資金計画までを網羅した完全マニュアルをお届けします。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "reference-eca789c7-45c9-48a3-a6b8-5328bf4a4e15",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-label-83ea2e1d-3a1c-400b-8cc9-62b2382bf9d2",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "参考: "
        },
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-link-9d542e64-bb97-4635-8549-6c85c2cd8bf9",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "link-b8851ef7-b132-4ef6-ba69-d7d07c6a75cf"
          ],
          "text": "厚生労働省 看護師等学校養成所卒業生就業状況調査"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-b8851ef7-b132-4ef6-ba69-d7d07c6a75cf",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/list/100-1.html"
        }
      ],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "823e0d34-c274-4189-b928-fe781e2a7c87",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "54d86665-2200-4a2f-8880-6d8622d00f6b",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "働きながら看護師を目指すための3つのルート"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "5a0a02f8-a66c-43ef-9071-bde51c9495c2",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "f5933325-3562-4fa9-bc81-49c9c423893b",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "社会人が看護師を目指す場合、主に3つのルートが考えられます。自分のライフプランや学力、経済状況に合わせて最適な道を選びましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "3847b426-b0eb-4e89-9f5e-345f5e77250b",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "a1e102e0-a993-4450-8f62-6ff4cc79f09f",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "ルート1：准看護師学校からステップアップ"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "a99fd890-7fab-4a36-b41b-d86a7e990510",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "31828bcb-aa9b-463f-bf63-463142f2221c-3029624e-91d1-461d-a5d4-90cfce474921",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "メリット"
        },
        {
          "_key": "31828bcb-aa9b-463f-bf63-463142f2221c-061b37e1-c416-4447-b9fd-a7dc20cb7ff9",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 働きながら通いやすい学校が多く、段階的にステップアップできる。准看護師として働きながら看護師を目指せる。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "reference-15777f72-6299-4978-9a0a-2f15b9e4a3b8",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-label-f577bacb-7fe9-45cd-83ec-ffe6141fbd5e",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "参考: "
        },
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-link-4e01a0c1-e8dd-4c22-a043-f0dcf3f7c6b5",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "link-f4b90df3-a61f-4a9c-9e69-7393c8c8faf1"
          ],
          "text": "日本看護協会 看護補助者の離職状況レポート"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-f4b90df3-a61f-4a9c-9e69-7393c8c8faf1",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.nurse.or.jp/home/assets/20231005_nl01.pdf?utm_source=chatgpt.com"
        }
      ],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "d0fe99bf-8e04-43fe-b74f-195da8cef954",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "3ef2a450-aca7-4a2b-95ae-41879617b8bf-c470c3d2-7086-4183-8ce7-2e36320c9a20",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "デメリット"
        },
        {
          "_key": "3ef2a450-aca7-4a2b-95ae-41879617b8bf-0807f36d-df0a-4d49-bb9c-cccb5534c630",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 看護師になるまでの総年数が長くなる。最終的に2回学校に通う必要がある。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "followup-444b8bed-d82c-40cb-b79b-a23de5107726",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "text-00837cfb-9876-431a-9bca-d6d2e9a15aa3",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "このように、ひとつずつ確認しながら進めることが大切です。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "reference-b7b6667b-b4f1-4cb8-b935-245a8b22b43f",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-label-706be5c7-7b52-419c-9934-d3c161b680d2",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "参考: "
        },
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-link-7ad90cb5-3261-4ee5-98d2-4ef9db29c48e",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "link-a63aa7c1-8dee-48f9-bb3d-fe11ea2729a4"
          ],
          "text": "厚生労働省 看護職員需給分科会"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-a63aa7c1-8dee-48f9-bb3d-fe11ea2729a4",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/seisakunitsuite/bunya/0000188411.html"
        }
      ],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "cd9cd65a-b578-4a09-a4f8-a4724bd6cb69",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "1c437742-2ac4-4ba6-999d-15c39dfb5343",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "ルート2：看護専門学校（定時制）"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "3621f66b-886e-4305-b199-5d3d595cf22c",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "913ced70-9d5b-4acd-8edc-6d14e809221a",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "週3〜4日、夜間などに授業を行う定時制の看護専門学校（3年）に通う方法です。昼間は病院で看護助手として働き、夜間に学びます。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "d9621da4-8f6f-4fdd-9925-4f769062be76",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "fe17701a-1193-4016-bba0-7004cdd5b317-cbe683f0-2a1e-46c1-a978-c826077ac74f",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "メリット"
        },
        {
          "_key": "fe17701a-1193-4016-bba0-7004cdd5b317-3e53db1b-a8ae-4712-956c-17fc6ac66350",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 昼間の収入を確保しながら、最短3年で看護師国家試験の受験資格を得られる。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "reference-7fc37400-9a55-4ddb-beaf-80454166c068",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-label-0fb8d2a2-ddd6-4b79-8db2-50cf98f022e5",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "参考: "
        },
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-link-b14f6d3e-6abc-407f-99d6-0cb505ec4ed0",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "link-4c2f241c-942f-4d9b-b31e-9429ceeaf405"
          ],
          "text": "厚生労働省 職業情報提供サイト（看護助手）"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-4c2f241c-942f-4d9b-b31e-9429ceeaf405",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://shigoto.mhlw.go.jp/User/Occupation/Detail/246?utm_source=chatgpt.com"
        }
      ],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "c896e58d-2af1-4745-aa5c-0c9ef8ea268b",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "ef7506ab-8f91-4c3e-8ecf-139152a38415-01a36171-a7d5-4eb4-875c-f67f4543bfa1",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "デメリット"
        },
        {
          "_key": "ef7506ab-8f91-4c3e-8ecf-139152a38415-6d6f49bc-45c5-45fc-a018-1230c1639ceb",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 仕事と学業の両立がハード。定時制の学校は数が限られている。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "followup-d1f900a6-36cf-474f-8fe9-523d4b0f8d25",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "text-c4ebe4ae-9183-45d7-9f84-487fcf194741",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "これらのポイントを押さえて、日々の業務に活かしていきましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "5b81fa2b-ae35-4d69-9053-b4dc3868ac90",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "12a7dd7c-d78a-4b7a-935e-bd3540814996",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "ルート3：看護専門学校・短大（通信制）"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "d843b6c1-4df6-4e6b-a92e-87de29c64aab",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "90c8c242-39e6-4156-b528-51e6047a6606",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "准看護師の資格を持っている方が対象となるルートです。通信制の看護師養成課程（2年）で、自宅学習とスクーリング（集合研修）を組み合わせて学びます。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "ed3498b8-f738-487c-b36d-c535b1f86bdd",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "3428b0ee-adb8-410f-a408-8ff9b4a01afc-2a437fa8-8c49-4595-876b-9240a9b75ba1",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "メリット"
        },
        {
          "_key": "3428b0ee-adb8-410f-a408-8ff9b4a01afc-99744cdb-be42-4326-a6f8-68f2a1aea551",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 自分のペースで学習を進めやすい。学費が比較的安い傾向にある。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "062eb625-6f32-4f55-9383-613bf2b193f8",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "1c08437c-aa09-4926-9238-5730898d83d6-0a33a983-7844-4491-98b0-4132c3f85273",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "デメリット"
        },
        {
          "_key": "1c08437c-aa09-4926-9238-5730898d83d6-7a90e845-7264-487d-be95-d340e40805b7",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 准看護師免許が必須。自己管理能力が強く求められる。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "section-closing-c7f8299c-1517-457d-8605-a5802f82cc62",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "section-closing-span-8074cf68-f4ec-404e-9c5f-4f8afbb09bff",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "働きながら看護師を目指すための3つのルートでは、看護師と連携しながら無理のない範囲で進めることが大切です。気になる点はその都度共有し、安全第一で取り組みましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "a5ecb944-ca89-42f7-b92b-0ae7aa789bc6",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "8309ebf5-f487-4095-9b20-2e6d664fdb74",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "看護学校入学に向けた具体的な準備"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "7b70cc21-98cf-41e6-a883-50e05eb69c84",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "b0f27859-0f96-4fba-a21f-fba113b74359",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "目指すルートを決めたら、次に入学試験に向けた準備を始めます。社会人入試は、学力試験に加えて、面接や小論文で「なぜ看護師になりたいのか」という強い意志が問われます。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "39cad17d-bef3-45cf-a661-f5870b1818f5",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "e839ae0d-d010-4405-bb86-56e9357da91e",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "情報収集：学校選びと説明会"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "41f8fdd5-88e8-4bdd-b161-f7b99d2b9586",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "33e033bf-22f4-433b-abd3-8299704e2f5d-fc8a7a16-007a-4398-b6a6-40f28d7c6f01",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "学校選びのポイント"
        },
        {
          "_key": "33e033bf-22f4-433b-abd3-8299704e2f5d-aec664fc-d0b6-460b-ade2-f4d75a5fabc6",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": カリキュラム、学費、通いやすさ、国家試験合格率、社会人学生の割合などを比較検討します。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "1f7c6757-5346-47bf-b7bd-d88be5c9a7e1",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "fb7c7416-bf74-4be4-a096-13c7ef93d57e-2af45d9e-e89e-42d3-a1c5-96734909d6c2",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "学校説明会・オープンキャンパス"
        },
        {
          "_key": "fb7c7416-bf74-4be4-a096-13c7ef93d57e-eb3b3549-4f7c-4b36-8daa-89c39e3cf858",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 多くの場合参加し、学校の雰囲気や先生、在校生の話を聞きましょう。個別相談で、働きながら通うことの現実について質問する絶好の機会です。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "followup-a20a7f82-c7dd-4b0c-b4f0-d4cc98c80a79",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "text-49f98ec7-8985-4b9f-84d5-003c58fb9d8d",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "これらを参考に、自分に合った方法を見つけてください。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "c2102bff-b3e7-4d6a-8c36-4416ff9428c9",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "4e223c4d-dc4c-4f68-bf0a-e7595c610118",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "試験対策：学力・小論文・面接"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
